title: Static Analysis

android.permission.READ_LOGS.description: Allows an application to read from the system's various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially including personal or private information.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH.description: Allows an application to view configuration of the local Bluetooth phone and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN.description: Allows an application to configure the local Bluetooth phone and to discover and pair with remote devices.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYS.description: Allows the application to mount and unmount file systems for removable storage.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA.description: Access extra location provider commands. Malicious applications could use this to interfere with the operation of the GPS or other location sources.

android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to change the state of network connectivity.

"heartRateHighDescription" : "La tachycardie sinusale : fréquente lors de gestes normaux, l’excitation, l’émotion, le tabagisme, la consommation d’alcool et de thé. Elle peut aussi être observée en cas de fièvre, de choc, d’anémie, d’hyperthyroïdie, d’insuffisance cardiaque et d’atropine, d’adrénaline et d’éphédrine."

"heartRateHigherDescription" : "La fréquence cardiaque de plus de 160 puls/min est principalement observée chez les patients souffrant de maladie cardiaque, souvent de palpitations, d’oppression thoracique, de gêne précordiale, de traitement précoce, et de traitement symptomatique."

"heartRateLowDescription" : "Bradycardie sinusale : Elle peut être observée dans le travail physique et chez les athlètes dans le long terme. C’est une pathologie remarquée dans les cas d’hypothyroïdie avec l’augmentation de la pression intracrânienne, la jaunisse obstructive, ou par l’overdose ou l’empoisonnement par le médicament digitalis, la quinidine ou le propranolol."

"heartRateLowerDescription" : "La fréquence cardiaque de moins de 40puls/min : c’est le cas, la plupart du temps, des patients atteints de maladies cardiaques qui ont souvent des palpitations, une oppression thoracique, une gêne précordiale. Il existe des exceptions : une fréquence cardiaque inférieure à 40puls/min pour les personnes en très bonne santé, qui font depuis longtemps des exercices physiques importants et dont le cœur a été renforcé et ayant donc des battements de cœur moins fréquents que la moyenne."

"heartRateStandDescription" : "La fréquence cardiaque d’un adulte en bonne santé et de 6 à 100 battements par minute, pour la majorité elle est de 60 à 80 battements par minute. La fréquence cardiaque est légèrement plus rapide pour les femmes."

"heartRateLowDescription" : "Bradicardia sinusale. "heartRateLowerDescription" : "La frequenza cardiaca inferiore a 40 volte, riscontrata soprattutto nei pazienti con malattie cardiache, spesso palpitazioni, tenuta di petto, disagio precordiale, dovrebbero essere controlli precoci, trattamento sintomatico. Esistono eccezioni: Frequenza cardiaca di meno di 40 volte ci sono alcune persone molto sane, a lungo impegnate in un lavoro fisico pesante e un intenso esercizio di persone, i loro cuori sono stati esercitati, il numero di battiti cardiaci è molto inferiore alle persone ordinarie."
"heartRateStandDescription" : "Frequenza cardiaca adulta sana da 60 a 100 volte/min, la maggior parte dei 60-80 battiti/min, le donne gradualmente più veloci."
"heartRateTestDescription" : "Il dispositivo rileverà la frequenza cardiaca in base al tipo di selezione"

"heartRateHighDescription" : "Sinus tachycardia gyakran megjelenik azoknál, akik épp edzeni voltak, izgatottak, vagy idegesek. Megtalálható még azoknál, akik dohányoznak, isznak, vagy koffeint fogyasztanak. Előfordul még azoknál, akik lázzasak, sokkosak, vérszegénységel küzdenek, pajzsmírigy túl működés esetén, szívproblémák fennállásakor, illetve a atropin, epinefrin vagy efedrint szedése szintén okozhatja ezt a jelenséget."

"heartRateLowDescription" : "Sinus bradycardia azon atlétáknál vagy személyeknél figyelhető meg, akik hosszútávú fizikai munkát végeznek. Ez a kondíció fennállhat hypothyreosis, a megnövekedett koponyaűri nyomás, az obstruktív sárgaság, digitalis, a kinidin vagy a propranolol gyógyszerekek mérgezése, vagy tuladagolása esetén."

"heartRateLowerDescription" : "A 40-nél kisebb pulzuszámot leggyakrabban szívbetegeknél látni. Ők gyakran tapasztalhatnak szívdobogás, mellkasi szorítás, mellkasi kényelmetlenség, és ajánlott a minél előbbi orvosi segítség kérése. A kivétel: annak az egészséges személynek, aki nehéz fizikai munkát végezett, vagy intenzív edzést tartott, szintén lehet 40-nél kisebb a pulzuszáma. Ebben az esetben az adott személy kondicionálta a szívét, hogy lassabban verjen, mint egy átlagembernek."
"heartRateStandDescription" : "Egy egészséges felnőtt személy pulzusa 60-100 között mozog. Az átlagos pulzus 60-80 lüktetés percenként. A nőknek általában magasabb a pulzusuk."

This application can track your body composition (BMI, body fat percentage, body water, bone mass, subcutaneous fat rate, visceral fat level, basal metabolic age, muscle mass, etc.), as well as cloud-based intelligent data analysis and tracking, providing perfect and healthy body composition analysis charts and reports. At the same time, the full support of the family is used together, so that you can know the health status of the family anytime and anywhere. It is connected to the sports intelligent bracelet, helps the regular fitness personnel to know more about the physical condition, is a good helper to use the user's health.
